                            <li>"What did you learn about your chosen career that surprised you?"</li>
                            <li>"What is one specific action you can take this month toward your career goals?"</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">Connection to Overall Objectives:</h4>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-2">
                            <li>Reinforce how today's activities build a foundation for career planning</li>
                            <li>Connect career planning to financial well-being</li>
                            <li>Highlight how early planning can lead to better long-term outcomes</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">Preview:</h4>
